   "body" : "This is a PR builds on #18038 to address remaining review comments.  \r\n\r\nThe unbroadcast set is a mechanism for the mempool to track locally submitted transactions (via wallet or RPC). The node does a best-effort of delivering the transactions to the network via retries every 10-15 minutes until either a `GETDATA` is received or the transaction is removed from the mempool.\r\n\r\nThis is a WIP PR. TODOs:\r\n- [ ] remove `nLastResend` logic https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/18038#discussion_r416826914\r\n- [ ] expose unbroadcast info via RPCs https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/18038#discussion_r416837980\r\n- [ ] add sanity check to verify unbroadcast txns still exist in mempool https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/18038#discussion_r416861609",
